name: Star Streaked Sky through a Turbulent Haze
description: This alien world has a thick atmosphere like Titan. Rich in organic materials called tholins, solar energetic particles occasionally power a beautiful aurora. Close to an open cluster, brilliant OB stars shine through the deep haze of the atmosphere. Yet in only 3-40 Myr their supernova will bathe this alien world in a sea of radiation. Should any inhabitants survive their mutations may become mighty.
